axta4ok00\n\n`129\nBugs found`\nF346555\n\n4. Go to try use query and write handle - ██████████\nF346562\n5. Go to profile and check \"Bugs found\" - `130`\nF346556\n6. Go to try use query @cisco and @apache\nF346559\nF346560\n7. Go to profile and check \"Bugs found\" -130\nF346557\n8. Go to try write █████████\nF346561\n9. Check \"Bugs found\" -`131`\nF346558\n\n██████ , ███████ have private page.\n\nIf after creating a report, this will be credited to your profile. So this program has a private page\n\nSorry i bad speak english\nI hope you understand me\nThank you,haxta4ok00\n\n## Impact\n\ndisclosure of external programs with private","bounty_amount":"3000.0","formatted_bounty":"$3,000","weakness":{"id":18,"name":"Information Disclosure"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":346555,"file_name":"129.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/346/555/1bfe2e22026df235c2477c193466d0a7a7394a08/129.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22129.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27129.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQYJPM5INV%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T093332Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIGPTFP%2F%2B61NRXKxUCRRiOEw%2FyEXMoJI30jSWgewoYzlYAiATW70r0%2Ft4BCmx%2BIRRvI9N9Vm6tq25cJqmqyf8P9oJnSq6BQjx%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMlnlVa%2Fn%2F5%2FBwcq%2BdKo4F1YnOHtgpcuOI6MB5pFrZ1JRxajUzrmu66Bs%2BaH059f9y01fPv%2FrjUZqEro3Jo9934IhhUwQj4gQeQ52XFU4tL%2Fl7ANAcg%2BweyQf%2FlO3JCodLg6QOdgOquP7BbCsXjast8Pomf8KP1lmk7IIMD7J9DS4cjH6SQasi3CttqywzFCaRrB8cbzZNYwGpMcshlGieMrYvXOKXlnFS%2Bvyupk%2BdoPGms%2F3cgeV%2BcDw50A71YHut794drWOwB%2BEgOIDnJqc%2FodmOUDjNrGX2PYH98D58CQI6kF0KLfi9CZmpJrhPYWDkdXTTag4OHihpyrvYSsSmxgEN1mpxlQWp3qqjt9qoTl0ks45f5BDGWqJfXqS6BToA%2FyYcov9sqsrq4OPo9l